{"tid":1587534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉~如果我今日大叫救人應該可以救返1個手足","createTime":"2019-09-22T12:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T20:45:38.000Z","uid":183950,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"147ee29f2144413fa6109054534b10672e23a436","tid":1587534,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:26:14.000Z","msg":"好想懺悔<br />\n沙田第1次火魔法30~60秒後撤退<br />\n有個防暴唔知邊到彈出黎係我隔離禁低左個<br />\n防暴大隊係後後面<br />\n如果我當時大叫救人應該夠人救到佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7b9c596c40a2e29681fe84582ab8ef004006ad","tid":1587534,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ce52bc764662dade65808130d1ea658a1eaf6f5","tid":1587534,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽到"},{"pid":"4ee46b15cc803a6eb1510b7caf2c80d22ab8fcf5","tid":1587534,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"如果你朋友大叫?"},{"pid":"21499d11e395e9f5f58160220ba23b10c9962479","tid":1587534,"uid":50874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"發埋d咁既夢既樓主你"},{"pid":"8e41f6fc58766d4a9fd867a5cbd3272448c0aaca","tid":1587534,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"學習再進化，求手足無事"},{"pid":"4a72698e77ec363c9168a8c0e07d7e60ada71bc3","tid":1587534,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"有個防暴<br />\n即係落單狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2e517a04ff403a245d3b571605c32716fa3677","tid":1587534,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=66102188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係<br />\n過去個兩個月正正常常係比應屆DSE同學仔溫書休息既<br />\n可惜呢個政府搞到大家奉獻左成個暑假，為左自己又好，為左將來又好，為左下一代又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有見連登上有多個關於網上問功課谷既需求，有見及此就有呢個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，免費網上問功課谷一直以唔張揚嘅方法存在。谷內有十多位Tutors (當中包括現職老師及名校畢業生在讀生)同DSE同學仔。形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直隱姓埋名係為左保障學生安全。但見到需求增加，又多左好多不同既補習post。所以我地希望提供俾同學多一個安全安心既選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2509d3f7582d64cc474153c6368212ef9112ee","tid":1587534,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5e44d543133dfd1839069bfac772cae109cc9f","tid":1587534,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"發生左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次果斷啲"},{"pid":"720f712e8b1a122c97f6aa0304317b413393c25f","tid":1587534,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5e44d543133dfd1839069bfac772cae109cc9f","tid":1587534,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"發生左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次果斷啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:45:38.000Z","msg":"但佢自己又唔大叫救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}